{"tid":1653683,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"《Silent Night in Hong Kong》","createTime":"2019-10-14T07:55:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T10:39:10.000Z","uid":163297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c61bc594e877a81d8bc515e8952d50e9ede4c9e4","tid":1653683,"uid":163297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:55:10.000Z","msg":"原曲：《Silent night》(平安夜)<br />\n詞：<br />\n<br />\nSilent night, tearing eyes<br />\nAll is cryin' , all is pale<br />\nWhen the people bleed for their freedoms <br />\nWhen the people die for their glory<br />\nWhen the most hopeless time comes<br />\nThere'll be a light in the dark<br />\n<br />\nSilent night, angry mind<br />\nAll is gas, all is spark<br />\nWhen the justice's not justice anymore<br />\nWhen the law-enforcer ignore the law<br />\nCan you hear the people sing <br />\nSinging for their anger<br />\n<br />\nLet the song, spread in the town<br />\nLet them know, we won't cede<br />\nWhen we fight for our freedoms<br />\nWhen we liberate for our town <br />\nIt's time for our revolution <br />\nFive demands not one less<br />\nFight for freedom stand with Hong Hong <br />\n<br />\n第一次開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲詞應該好教會feel，原諒我垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果大家對歌詞有更好提議<br />\n歡迎討論<br />\n求大家屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"7bdf1fe1138decf1f880e90d56aab1504e17fb0c","tid":1653683,"uid":322141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:56:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1747e5e0181dddb09dc657fc126a5efbdfc64fe4","tid":1653683,"uid":163297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:56:57.000Z","msg":"推下"},{"pid":"5d5823323107725d2c70e1273c62147eef